# Changelog

## [2.4.12] - 2025-11-27
### Added
- Background removal with multiple AI methods
- Temporary email system with inbox checking
- Interactive menu with button navigation
- IP geolocation with accurate user detection

### Fixed
- Location detection showing server IP instead of user IP
- Email inbox reception issues
- Menu pagination and session management
- Image processing reliability

### Changed
- Improved error handling and fallback mechanisms
- Enhanced user experience with reaction system
- Optimized performance and memory usage